### 步骤1: 启动带人工干预的订单处理工作流 (订单金额>1000触发失败)
POST https://localhost:5001/order-processing-manual
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "PROD-MANUAL",
  "quantity": 10,
  "couponCode": "DISCOUNT10",
  "orderAmount": 1500.00,
  "userId": "USER-MANUAL"
}

# 响应会包含工作流ID,例如: "WorkflowInstanceId: abc-123-def"
# 工作流会暂停并等待人工审批

###
### 步骤2: 审批通过 - 执行补偿 (需要替换workflowInstanceId)
POST https://localhost:5001/approve-compensation?workflowInstanceId=YOUR_WORKFLOW_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

true

###
### 步骤2备选: 审批拒绝 - 不执行补偿 (需要替换workflowInstanceId)
POST https://localhost:5001/approve-compensation?workflowInstanceId=YOUR_WORKFLOW_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

false

